    "\", it would be clear that ARI is not being addressed from just the text.",
    "In order to measure how effective gaze information is to determine the addressee in our specific setting, we annotated real MPCs collected in the hospital.",
    "We have video recordings of the interactions with the robot's cameras and an external camera.",
    "Using both the video and audio, the gold addressee of each turn was annotated along with whether the user was looking at ARI or not.",
    "Using the Vicuna-13b-v1.5 LLM (Chiang et al., 2023), we created two addressee detectors."
